{"word":"H4288 - מְחִתָּה - mᵉchittâh - mekh-it-taw' - Destruction","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מְחִתָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mᵉchittâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mekh-it-taw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Destruction"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பாழ், கேடு, வறுமை, கலக்கம், முறிவு, அழிவு, திகில், திகைப்பு, பயங்கரம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"destruction, ruin, terror, a breaking"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H2846 - חָתָה - châthâh - khaw-thaw'/2846\">H2846</a>; properly a <i>dissolution</i>; concretely a <i>ruin</i>, or (abstractly) <i>consternation: - </i>destruction, dismaying, ruin, terror."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2844 - חַת - chath - khath/2844\">H2844</a>, <a href=\"#/H2847 - חִתָּה - chittâh - khit-taw'/2847\">H2847</a>, <a href=\"#/H2849 - חַתְחַת - chathchath - khath-khath'/2849\">H2849</a>, <a href=\"#/H2851 - חִתִּית - chittîyth - khit-teeth'/2851\">H2851</a>, <a href=\"#/H2865 - חָתַת - châthath - khaw-thath'/2865\">H2865</a>, <a href=\"#/H2866 - חֲתַת - chăthath - khath-ath'/2866\">H2866</a>, <a href=\"#/H2867 - חֲתַת - Chăthath - khath-ath'/2867\">H2867</a>, <a href=\"#/H4288 - מְחִתָּה - mᵉchittâh - mekh-it-taw'/4288\">H4288</a>"}]}